  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to review the CCU 8775 schematic with respect to SAIL"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "SAIL IOs"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Only 78 SAIL_IOs from SA8775P are routed to QAM8775P BGA. SAIL_IO_63 is not routed, and it is for internal use only"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Check SAIL_IO_47 and SAIL_IO_49 with HW team, may be the data sheet we use is old"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For USS, HW connection is ok, But better to check in detail"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Key Inputs to SAIL"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "5 CANs",
        "Ethernet",
        "OSPI",
        "UART to SCC, UART to debug board",
        "USS",
        "GPIO to SCC"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Schematic is reviewed with 80-42841-1_REV_AG_QAM8775P_Data_Sheet"
